title: Slim Thug and DJ Webstar talks Corona Virus Symptoms
itunes:title: Slim Thug and DJ Webstar talks Corona Virus Symptoms
description:
Today on the show we had Slim Thug and Dj Webstar who both was tested positive for the Corona Virus call in to the show, where they each spoke about their symptoms before testing and how they are recovering and preventing the virus getting worse. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Dan Patrick from his viral plea to let grandparents sacrifice themselves and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee" where one listener needed help telling his wife about his past dealing with the same sex.
